      "message": "Redfish has https://redfish.dmtf.org/schemas/v1/EnvironmentMetrics.v1_6_0.json \n\nFrom https://redfish.dmtf.org/redfish/mockups/v1/1819\n```\n\"PowerWatts\":view details {\n  \"Reading\":view details 374,\n  \"DataSourceUri\":view details \"/redfish/v1/Chassis/1U/Sensors/TotalPower\"} ,\n\"PowerLimitWatts\":view details {\n  \"SetPoint\":view details 500,\n  \"AllowableMax\":view details 1000,\n  \"AllowableMin\":view details 150,\n  \"ControlMode\":view details \"Automatic\",\n  \"DataSourceUri\":view details \"/redfish/v1/Chassis/1U/Controls/PowerLimit\"} ,\n```\n\nIs there any advice from Redfish on when to use MinPowerWatts / MaxPowerWatts here and when to use EnvironmentMetrics ?",
